d_graph <-
  c_graph %>%
  add_node(
    type = "type_a",
    node_aes = node_aes(
      color = "steelblue",
      fillcolor = "lightblue",
      fontcolor = "gray35"
    ),
    node_data = node_data(
      value = 2.5
    )
  ) %>%
  add_edge(
    from = 1, to = 3,
    rel = "interacted_with",
    edge_aes = edge_aes(
      color = "red",
      arrowhead = "vee",
      tooltip = "Red Arrow"
    ),
    edge_data = edge_data(
      value = 5.2
    )
  )

i_graph_1 %>% is_graph_empty()

add_nodes_from_table() table nodes

# Add the nodes to the graph
i_graph_2 <-
  i_graph_1 %>%
  add_nodes_from_table(
    table = node_list_1,
    label_col = label
  )

j_graph <- 
  create_graph() %>% 
  add_nodes_from_table(
    table = node_list_2,
    label_col = label,
    type_col = type
  ) %>%
  add_edges_from_table(
    table = edge_list_2,
    from_col = from,
    to_col = to,
    from_to_map = id_external,
    rel_col = rel
  ) %>%
  drop_node_attrs(node_attr = id_external)

nodes edges node attributesvalue_1 value_2

  -- directed / connected / property graph / simple

node/edge metadatanodes edges value_1 value_2 mutate_node_attrs() mutate_edge_attrs() value_1 value_2 value_3 nodes edges value_3 10 nodes edges forestgreen red`` nodes value_3` 

k_graph <-
  j_graph %>%
  mutate_node_attrs(value_3 = value_1 + value_2) %>%
  mutate_edge_attrs(value_3 = value_1 + value_2) %>%
  select_nodes(conditions = value_3 > 10) %>%
  set_node_attrs_ws(node_attr = fillcolor, value = "forestgreen") %>%
  invert_selection() %>%
  set_node_attrs_ws(node_attr = fillcolor, value = "red") %>%
  select_edges(conditions = value_3 > 10) %>%
  set_edge_attrs_ws(edge_attr = color, value = "forestgreen") %>%
  invert_selection() %>%
  set_edge_attrs_ws(edge_attr = color, value = "red") %>%
  clear_selection() %>%
  set_node_attr_to_display(attr = value_3)
render_graph(k_graph)

  add_edge(
    from = "Kim",
    to = "stringbuildeR",
